[Student "S"]
{NORTH might well bid 3NT at his second turn, and this may turn out to be the 
final contract anyway.

But it doesn't hurt to bid 2\D (Fourth Suit Forcing) just to 
see if SOUTH happens to have three \Ss. She does, so 4\S becomes the better game.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "E:85.QJ97.AQ9.A843 JT.632.T87.KJT76 AK763.KT84.K4.52 Q942.A5.J6532.Q9"]
